title: [FSX/P3D] IRIS Pro Series - Silence Twister v3.0
description:
IRIS Silence Twister v3.0 for you pirates.

This aircraft, which is now withdrawn from sale due to some legal issues, was criticised a lot when first released due to not living up to its hype. IRIS later released several patches to rectify the issues, but unfortunately they never made it to you guys. Now you all can enjoy it.

This aircraft worked in P3D v2 on a few computers we tested it, so the installer and additional tools that came with the installer were rebuild with P3D v2 installation option in mind, however NO warranty for P3D v2 compatibility on your computer is guaranteed. Try it in P3D v2 at your own risk.

SEED and enjoy!
